效益与人工成本情况 - ADS

taskParams.sql:
/***********************************************************
任务名称：ADS_HR_COST_PROFIT
功能描述：
运行频率：每 N 分钟/小时/天 一次
输入表：
输出表：
加载策略：3 （注：1-全表覆盖 ，2-增量更新，3-增量追加）
创建时间：2024-11-19 15:25:15
创建人：zhangch2
修改历史：
版本          更改日期          更改人             修改说明

***********************************************************/
truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_COST_PROFIT;

insert into
    ads${env}.ADS_HR_COST_PROFIT (
        biz_year,
        org_cn_abbr,
        tot_cost,
        gross_prof,
        net_prof,
        biz_income,
        labor_cost,
        labor_cost_yoy,
        wages,
        wages_yoy,
        wrks,
        wages_per_cap,
        productivity,
        labor_cost_ratio,
        labor_cost_ratio_yoy,
        prof_mrgn,
        prof_mrgn_yoy,
        labor_prop,
        labor_prop_yoy,
        org_cd,
        biz_date
    )
with
    t as (
        select
            *,
            100 * labor_cost / gross_revenue as labor_cost_ratio, -- 人事费用率
            100 * gross_profit / labor_cost as prof_mrgn, -- 人工成本利润率
            100 * labor_cost / total_cost as labor_prop, -- 人工成本占总成本比例
            wages / mean_employees as wages_per_cap, -- 平均工资
            total_productivity / workforce as productivity -- 全员劳动生产率
        from
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_XYYRGCBQK
    )
select
    biz_year,
    org_name as org_cn_abbr,
    total_cost as tot_cost,
    gross_profit as gross_prof,
    net_profit as net_prof,
    gross_revenue as biz_income,
    labor_cost,
    100 * (
        labor_cost / lag (labor_cost, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_name
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as labor_cost_yoy,
    wages,
    100 * (
        wages / lag (wages, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_name
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as wages_yoy,
    employees as wrks,
    wages_per_cap,
    productivity,
    labor_cost_ratio,
    100 * (
        labor_cost_ratio / lag (labor_cost_ratio, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_name
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as labor_cost_ratio_yoy,
    prof_mrgn,
    100 * (
        prof_mrgn / lag (prof_mrgn, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_name
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as prof_mrgn_yoy,
    labor_prop,
    100 * (
        labor_prop / lag (labor_prop, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_name
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as labor_prop_yoy,
    org_code as org_cd,
    null as biz_date
from
    t

taskParams.sql:
/***********************************************************
任务名称：SQL
功能描述：
运行频率：每 N 分钟/小时/天 一次
输入表：
输出表：
加载策略：3 （注：1-全表覆盖 ，2-增量更新，3-增量追加）
创建时间：2024-11-20 15:09:10
创建人：zhangch2
修改历史：
版本          更改日期          更改人             修改说明

***********************************************************/
truncate table dw${env}.DWD_HR_XYYRGCBQK;

insert into
    dw${env}.DWD_HR_XYYRGCBQK (
        biz_year,
        org_name,
        org_code,
        total_cost,
        gross_profit,
        net_profit,
        gross_revenue,
        labor_cost,
        wages,
        employees,
        mean_employees,
        total_productivity,
        workforce,
        employee_cost
    )
with
    clear as (
        select
            *,
            zgrs_e as 职工人数,
            zgpjrs_k as 职工平均人数, -- = 职工人数
            CYRYPJRS_C as 从业人员平均人数,
            cast(
                aes_decrypt (
                    unhex (yyzcb_z),
                    'F3M0PxSWod6cyCejYUkpccU9gMsWwgrM'
                ) as double
            ) as 营业总成本,
            cast(
                aes_decrypt (
                    unhex (lrze_f),
                    'F3M0PxSWod6cyCejYUkpccU9gMsWwgrM'
                ) as double
            ) as 利润总额,
            cast(
                aes_decrypt (unhex (jlr_u), 'F3M0PxSWod6cyCejYUkpccU9gMsWwgrM') as double
            ) as 净利润,
            cast(
                aes_decrypt (
                    unhex (yyzsr_e),
                    'F3M0PxSWod6cyCejYUkpccU9gMsWwgrM'
                ) as double
            ) as 营业总收入,
            cast(
                aes_decrypt (
                    unhex (qyrgcb_k),
                    'F3M0PxSWod6cyCejYUkpccU9gMsWwgrM'
                ) as double
            ) as 企业人工成本,
            cast(
                aes_decrypt (
                    unhex (sfzggzze_x),
                    'F3M0PxSWod6cyCejYUkpccU9gMsWwgrM'
                ) as double
            ) as 实发职工工资总额,
            cast(
                aes_decrypt (
                    unhex (ldsczz_e),
                    'F3M0PxSWod6cyCejYUkpccU9gMsWwgrM'
                ) as double
            ) as 劳动生产总值,
            cast(
                aes_decrypt (
                    unhex (ZGRGCB_S),
                    'F3M0PxSWod6cyCejYUkpccU9gMsWwgrM'
                ) as double
            ) as 职工人工成本
        from
            ods${env}.ODS_HR_XYYRGCBQK
    )
select
    nd_s as biz_year,
    coalesce(zgqy_t, '') as org_name,
    coalesce(zzdm_j, '') as org_code,
    营业总成本 as total_cost,
    利润总额 as gross_profit,
    净利润 as net_profit,
    营业总收入 as gross_revenue,
    企业人工成本 as labor_cost,
    实发职工工资总额 as wages,
    职工人数 as employees,
    职工平均人数 as mean_employees,
    劳动生产总值 as total_productivity,
    从业人员平均人数 as workforce,
    职工人工成本 as employee_cost
from
    clear

truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_BENCHMARK;

insert into
    ads${env}.ADS_HR_BENCHMARK (
        biz_year,
        org_cn_abbr,
        indictrs_type,
        indictrs,
        bench_p50,
        bench_quantile,
        org_cd
    )
with
    cd as (
        select distinct
            org_name,
            org_code
        from
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_XYYRGCBQK
    )
select
    nd_n as biz_year,
    ZGQY_L as org_cn_addr,
    case xyfl_q
        when '1' then '人事费用率'
        when '2' then '人工成本利润率'
        when '3' then '人工成本占比'
    end as indictrs_type,
    rsfy_rgcb_rate as indictrs,
    xy50fwz_s as bench_p50,
    xydbfwz_y as bench_quantile,
    org_code as org_cd
from
    ods${env}.ODS_HR_XNQK as xn
    left join cd on cd.org_name = xn.ZGQY_L

修改历史：

***********************************************************/
truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_DISBURSEMENT;

INSERT INTO
    ads${env}.ADS_HR_DISBURSEMENT (org_cn_abbr, grnt_amount, org_cd)
with
    t as (
        select
            *,
            row_number() over (
                partition by
                    org_code
                order by
                    biz_year desc,
                    cast(biz_month as int) desc
            ) as k
        from
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_YFXYYRGCBQK
    )
select
    org_name,
    wages,
    org_code
from
    t
where
    k = 1
